Dear NewJeans Members,

I hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to let you know how much I support you all during this challenging time. **Hanni,** your vibrant energy and enthusiasm are infectious. I love how you bring such a unique spark to the group with your lively personality and dedication. Your passion for performing and your ability to light up the stage are genuinely appreciated.ğŸ’—

*Danielle your elegance and versatility shine through in everything you do. Whether youâ€™re singing or dancing, you bring a level of professionalism and grace that captivates everyone. Your hard work and talent are inspiring and Iâ€™m thankful for the beauty you add to the group.ğŸ’›

**Haerin,** I am constantly impressed by your powerful voice and emotional depth. Your performances are always moving, and your commitment to perfecting your craft is clear. Your contributions to the group are invaluable, and I appreciate everything you do.ğŸ’š

**Hyein,** your youthful energy and charm bring a fresh perspective to the group. I admire how you balance fun with professionalism, and your enthusiasm is truly refreshing. Iâ€™m excited to see all the wonderful things you will achieve in the future.ğŸ’œ

Your music and performances have had a profound impact on my life, and for that, I am deeply grateful. The joy, comfort, and inspiration you bring through your work are invaluable. No matter what decisions you make or the paths you choose, please know that you have a loyal and supportive community behind you. We appreciate everything you do and are here to support you, no matter what.

With heartfelt support and admiration,
